Simple,Visa,API,is,an,on,demand,international,travel,authorization,platform,that,can,be,integrated,to,business,applications,This,system,works,with,countries,that,offer,electronic,visas,or,travel,authorizations,SimpleVisa,offers,an,API,which,supports,several,features,including,requesting,an,authorization,quote,creating,an,authorization,and,polling,the,API,to,know,the,status,of,the,authorization,This,REST,API,uses,JSON,for,data,exchange,and,requires,HTTP,Basic,Authentication